{
  "stem": "20710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I lived-- when I was in the basement in his house, I came down with a very high temperature.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was there for about three days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I couldn't stay there anymore, because this was a very infectious-- you know, it was, anyway, already-- practically everybody went through this, from the not being clean or what.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think lice or whatever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They said that lice bring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't happen to have them, but they bring the infection, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyhow, I came down with high temperature.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he-- they couldn't keep me there, and, and these-- there was a few Jewish guys that were also supervising this field work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, they're-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so they, they were very nice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they also could travel between Kurowice and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they took me back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was a hospital that they used to take in all these sick people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I said, I don't want to go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they didn't want to put me there, because many times they came and whoever was with all these infectious disease, they used to, you know-- they used to finish them off there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They used to kill them there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they took me back to-- my father was still in, in this place where he lived, that I don't know how many families lived in this place.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he took me there, and I was there for about 14 days, this took, you know, this high temperature and all this was going on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And nothing to eat, and I couldn't eat, I couldn't drink.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Anyway, it's-- I was just-- you know, this was for 14 days.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
